fields.title: This is the beginning of an awesome story.
fields.summary: In the beginning, there is a man who starves of awesomeness. Until he found a great tool. He didn't know what the tool was. Until he figured how to to use it.
fields.content:
In the beginning, there is a man who starves of awesomeness. Until he found a great tool. He didn't know what the tool was. Until he figured how to to use it.

The more often he used the tool, the more passion sparks towards using it. He became creative the more he used it. It seems he's just playing as he was willing to use it all day.

Later he named the tool, Django.
